🚨 Sweepstakes rules ⬇️
You must FOLLOW ALL sponsoring Instagram accounts I am following NOW to be eligible. This contest begins on 28th July 2021 at 7pm PST and ends 30th July 2021 at 7pm PST. I will then ARCHIVE MY POST to avoid confusion. COMMENTS on this post, Kylie's post & CB's post are all VALID. Private accounts must be made PUBLIC until the winner is announced. Winner must post the ‘I WON’ image on their page.  Full sweepstake T&Cs linked in my bio. 

The winner will be announced at www.curatedbusinesses.com (you can see all past winners there too) + under this image on the @curatedbusinesses Instagram page by August 6th,  2021. 
.
.
Please Note: This sweepstakes is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram or the BRANDS shown in this image. By entering, entrants confirm they are 18+ years of age, release Instagram of responsibility, and agree to Instagram's term of use. No purchase necessary. VOID WHERE PROHIBITED BY LAW : �
